contest.metaDescription: Are you a Kabaddi Pro, play our Quiz Game and win prizes daily, weekly and a grand winner, running parallel to season 5 of the prokabaddi league. As the twelve teams Bengal Warriors, Bengaluru Bulls, Dabang Delhi, U Mumba, Puneri Paltan, Patna Pirates, Jaipur Pink Panther, Telugu Titans, Haryana Steelers, battle out on the mat, you can battle out on your very own arena daily.
